# Complex Node Formatting

Represents a `Complex` literal (that returns an `Complex` number)
<!-- END_AUTOGENERATED -->

## Formats a Complex literal

Before:

```ruby
1i
```

After:

```ruby
1i
```

## Formats a complex literal in an expression

Before:

```ruby
2+1i
```

After:

```ruby
2+1i
```
